30020000.Original_Text: 준비가 끝나신 분은 탑승 수속을 \n완료해주시기 바랍니다!
30020000.English_Text:
If you are ready, 
please complete the boarding procedure!
30020000.Chinese_Text:
如果您准备好了,请完成
登机手续!

30020001.Original_Text: 다시 배가 망가지는 일은 없어야 할 텐데...
30020001.English_Text: You shouldn't have to ruin your stomach again...
30020001.Chinese_Text: 我不想我的胃再次破裂...

30020002.Original_Text: 아, 누님. 그러지말고 조금만 나눠주세요.\n하루 이틀 본 사이도 아닌데...
30020002.English_Text:
Oh, sister. Please don't do that, share a little.
We haven't seen each other in a day or two...
30020002.Chinese_Text:
哦,修女.请不要那样做,请分享一点.
我们已经一两天没见了……

30020003.Original_Text: 에헤이. 나도 어렵게 구한 거라니까 그러네?\n이제 좀 그만 보채게!
30020003.English_Text:
Hey. It's because I got it too hard, right?
Now stop staring!
30020003.Chinese_Text:
嘿是不是因为我也遇到了困难? 
 不要盯着我看!

30020004.Original_Text: <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>수양</> 녀석들은 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>거미줄</>을 공급해 준다더니\n왜 아직도 소식이 없는 거야!?
30020004.English_Text:
<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Weeping</> niggas said they supply <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>Cobweb</>
Why is there still news? You don't have one!?
30020004.Chinese_Text:
<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>他们说要提供<textColor=[255:204:102:255]>蜘蛛网</>.
为什么还没有消息!?

30020005.Original_Text: <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>에레다</> 문파는 요즘 통 보이질 않네.\n<textColor=[110:216:175:255]>예도항</>에는 오지 않기로 한 건가?
30020005.English_Text:
<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Ereda</> I can't see the clan these days.
<textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Yedohang</> Have you decided not to come?
30020005.Chinese_Text:
<textColor=[78:148:215:255]> 艾瑞达</> 家族这几天没有出现 
 <textColor=[110:216:175:255]> 决定不来夜都港</>了吗?

30020006.English_Text:
Come here~!
What are you looking for?

30020007.English_Text: Um... it doesn't seem like it...

30020008.Original_Text: 이거 원, 직접 가서 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>거미줄</>을 구해야 하나?
30020008.English_Text: I won this, should I go and get the <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>Cobweb</>?
30020008.Chinese_Text: 就是这个了,我要不要去拿<textColor=[255:204:102:255]>蜘蛛网</>?

30020009.English_Text:
It's been a month since I haven't tasted <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>Douglasgrass</>...
<textColor=[255:204:102:255>Dog...all...rae...full...</>Nyan...
30020009.Chinese_Text:
<textColor=[255:204:102:255]> 盖达莱草 </> 已经有一个月没吃过了... 
 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]> 盖...

30020010.English_Text:
Hmm...the stock seems to be out of stock?
How about this...
30020010.Chinese_Text:
嗯...我猜那里有很多存货? 
 这个怎么样...

30020011.Original_Text: <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>녹각다귀</>는 <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>거점 북부</>에 널려있습니다.\n못 찾는 게 이상할 정도라니까요?
30020011.English_Text:
<textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Anger gnats</> are scattered around <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Northern Point</>.
You can't find them It's kind of weird, isn't it?

30020013.English_Text:
The morale of the <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Crew</> doesn't make sense.
<textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Reinforcement from home</> Are you saying he's an agent...
30020013.Chinese_Text:
<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>成员</>的士气没有意义 
 <textColor=[110:216:175:255]> 来自祖国的援军</>只是代理人……

30020014.Original_Text: <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>감시탑</>의 남겨진 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>물자</>를 옮겨야 하는데...\n하, 다들 바쁘니 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>용병</>이라도 써야 하는 건가?
30020014.English_Text:
The <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Watchtower</> leftover <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>Material</> needs to be moved...
Ha , Everyone is busy, so should I use <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Mercenary</>?
30020014.Chinese_Text:
<textColor=[110:216:175:255]>我需要移动瞭望塔剩余的<textColor=[255:204:102:255]>材料</></>…… 
哈,大家都很忙<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>有必要使用佣兵</>吗?

30020015.Original_Text: 이런 쥐꼬리만 한 녹으로 어떻게 집을 사?
30020015.English_Text: How do you buy a house with this little rattle rust?
30020015.Chinese_Text: 这么小锈怎么能买房子呢?

30020017.Original_Text: <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>혈비의 숲</>이라고 했습니까? 허허, 이거 참.\n그래서 지금 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>단원</>들이 찾고 있다구요?
30020017.English_Text:
Did you say <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Blood Forest</>? Heh heh, this is true.
So now <textColor=[78:148:215:255]> Are you looking for members</>?
30020017.Chinese_Text:
你说的是<textColor=[110:216:175:255]>血林</>吗?呵呵,原来如此.
那么现在<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>单位</>在找吗?

30020018.Original_Text: 일이 그렇게 되었습니다....\n그, 이번에 들어온 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>신입</> 있지 않습니까.
30020018.English_Text:
That's what happened....
Hey, isn't there a <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>rookie</> who came in this time?
30020018.Chinese_Text:
事情是这样的…… 
这次不是有<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>新员工</>进来吗?

30020019.Original_Text: 섣불리 움직였다가는... 낭패를 보겠군요.\n알겠습니다. 방도를 찾아보지요.
30020019.English_Text:
If you move too quickly... you'll be in trouble.
Okay. Let's find a way.
30020019.Chinese_Text:
如果你过早地搬家……你会遇到麻烦的.
我明白了.让我们想办法.

30020020.English_Text:
You mean if you wait here...?
<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Chief</>what do you think?

30020021.Original_Text: <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>단장</>님 생각대로 일이 진행되려나...?\n에이 됐다. 나는 그냥 시키는대로 하면 되겠지.
30020021.English_Text:
<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Chief</>Is this going to go the way you thought...?
It's okay. I'll just do what I'm told.
30020021.Chinese_Text:
<textColor=[78:148:215:255]> 经理</> 会不会像你想的那样...? 
 是的.我只会做我被告知的

30020022.Original_Text: 아이고 무릎이야...\n<textColor=[215:94:94:255]>운반해</> 녀석이 그래도 살려는 줬네. 다행이다...
30020022.English_Text:
Oh my, it's a knee...
<textColor=[215:94:94:255]>carry it</> He said he was still alive. I'm glad...
30020022.Chinese_Text:
哎呀,是我的膝盖... 
<textColor=[215:94:94:255]> 执行它 </> 他说他还想活下去.感谢上帝...

30020023.Original_Text: 그래도 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>수양</>이랑 원만히 지내야 좋을 텐데...\n생각했던 대로 흘러가지 않아 걱정이구만.
30020023.English_Text:
Still, it would be nice to get along with <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Weeping</>...
I'm worried that things aren't going the way I expected.

30020024.Original_Text: 참 흥미로운 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>소협</>이야.\n나도 저럴 때가 있었는데! 힘내자 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>곽호룡</>!
30020024.English_Text:
It's a very interesting <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>Shortcut</>.
I used to be like that too! Let's do our best <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Kwak Ho-ryong</>!
30020024.Chinese_Text:
很有趣的<textColor=[255:204:102:255]>小帮</>.
我也有过这样的经历!努力吧<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>郭浩龙</>!

30020025.Original_Text: <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>늪지</>로 갔던 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>일꾼</>들은 왜 오지 않는 거지?\n혹시 무슨 일이라도 당한 건가...
30020025.English_Text:
Why don't the <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>workers</> workers who went to <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Swamp</> come?
Maybe Did something happen...
30020025.Chinese_Text:
<textColor=[110:216:175:255]>为什么去沼泽</>的<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>工人</>没有来?
是不是发生了什么事……

30020026.English_Text:
<textColor=[255:204:102:255]>It's called a kaleidoscope</>... I've only seen how to make it in a book...
Ugh, I'm nervous.
30020026.Chinese_Text:
<textColor=[255:204:102:255]>叫做万花筒</>……我只在书里看到过怎么做…… 
呃,我很紧张.

30020027.Original_Text: 휴... 성공했어! 근데 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>신수</>를 부르는 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>제사</>라니...\n 듣던 대로 대단한 <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>소협</>이네.
30020027.English_Text:
Phew... you succeeded! But <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>Jesus</> calling <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Sacred Beast</> ...
 As I've heard, <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>Small</>
30020027.Chinese_Text:
哇……你做到了!但是,<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>有唱神兽</>的<textColor=[255:204:102:255]>仪式</>…… 
听说是很棒的<textColor=[255:204:102:255]>小型演唱会</>.

30020029.English_Text:
Oh! You guys! I don't know!?
<textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Didn't we meet at Half Moon Lake</>!?
30020029.Chinese_Text:
哦!你!不知道!?
<textColor=[110:216:175:255]>我们不是在汪达尔湖</>见过的吗?!

30020030.English_Text:
Please save me!
<textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Snake mushroom</> is so scary!

30020031.English_Text:
Thank you!
You are a lifesaver!
30020031.Chinese_Text:
非常感谢!
这是救命稻草!

30020032.Original_Text: 다음부터는 일행이랑 떨어지지 말거라.\n<textColor=[255:204:102:255]>소협</>이 아니었으면 큰일 날 뻔했구나.
30020032.English_Text:
Next time, don't leave your party with your party.
If it wasn't for <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>Cool</>, it would have been a big mess.
30020032.Chinese_Text:
下一次,不要和你的聚会一起离开.如果不是
<textColor=[255:204:102:255]>小组</>,那就是一件大事了.

30020033.English_Text:
Tell me when you're ready
This <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>old man</> must also be ready.

30020034.Original_Text: 어쩌다 이런 길을 선택한 것입니까...\n<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>에레다</> 역사상 최고의 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>문주</>라고 생각했는데...
30020034.English_Text:
How did you choose this path...
<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Ereda</> Best <textColor=[78:148:215:255]> I thought it was Moonju</>...
30020034.Chinese_Text:
你是怎么选择这条路的... 
 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]> Ereda </> 我认为这是历史上最好的<textColor=[78:148:215:255]> Munju </>...

30020035.English_Text:
Are you feeling a little better?
You should have done it in moderation. Be careful.
30020035.Chinese_Text:
你的身体感觉好一点了吗? 
 你应该适度地做.当心.

30020036.English_Text:
Yes... Thanks for your concern, I'm fine.
I'll be more careful next time!
30020036.Chinese_Text:
是的……谢谢关心,我没事.
下次我会小心的!

30020037.Original_Text: 아이고, 이게 무슨 일이야.\n웬 <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>환영</>들이 이렇게나 많은 거야!?
30020037.English_Text:
Hey, what's going on here.
Why are there so many <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Welcome</>!?
30020037.Chinese_Text:
哦,天哪,这是什么?
为什么有这么多<textColor=[215:94:94:255]>欢迎</>!?

30020038.Original_Text: 용케 찾아온 것을 보니 아주 애송이는 아니구나.\n마음의 준비는 되었느냐.
30020038.English_Text:
Looking like you've come so often, it's not like you're a very childish girl.
Are you mentally ready?
30020038.Chinese_Text:
看他来得这么频繁,已经不是小孩子了.
你做好心理准备了吗?

30020040.English_Text:
It's been a while~ <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Moonju</>.
What's going on with you saying you're coming soon?

30020042.Original_Text: 감사합니다. 덕분에 한시름 덜었습니다.\n제가 <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>연구 대원</>들에게 전하겠습니다.
30020042.English_Text:
Thank you. Thanks for saving an hour.
I'll pass it on to the <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Researchers</>.
30020042.Chinese_Text:
谢谢你.多亏了你,我节省了一个小时.
我会转告<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>研究人员</>.

30020043.English_Text: Uh, I think this <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Biryuha</>the death penalty left?
30020043.Chinese_Text: 呃,这个好像是<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>飞流羽</>刽子手留下的吧?

30020044.English_Text: Why are you here. Get away from it.

30020045.English_Text:
My, I'll protect you.
Don't fall from your side!
30020045.Chinese_Text:
我会保护你的.
不要从侧面掉下来!

30020046.English_Text:
Uh huh... that's all I want.
When will I get the <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>Illusion Soul Fire</>?
30020046.Chinese_Text:
呃……那你什么时候能拿到韩元
<textColor=[255:204:102:255]>迎魂佛</>?

30020047.English_Text:
<textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Steel Fist</>...
Go and <textColor=[255:204:102:255]>Essence of Thunderwood</> Save me.

30020048.English_Text:
Yeah! No that's...
That's it, so <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Tobacco</> next to <textColor=[215:94:94:255]> Welcome</>this!
30020048.Chinese_Text:
好的!不,那是... 
 那,所以 <textColor=[215:94:94:255]> Toyeoncho </> 紧挨着 <textColor=[215:94:94:255]> 欢迎 </>!

30020049.Chinese_Text: 哈...它是多种多样的,真的.
